    .build()
    .loadConfigOrThrow<MyConfig>()
  ```
  
  ### PropsPropertySource
  
  To use a java.util.Properties object as property source, we can use the `PropsPropertySource` implementation.
  
  ```kotlin
  ConfigLoaderBuilder.default()
    .addSource(PropsPropertySource(myProps))
    .build()
